 The National Sliding Center in Yanqing competition zone of Beijing 2022 shows its beauty after snow. The FIL Luge International Training Week in Yanqing started on Nov. 7 in the first snow of Beijing this winter. Athletes from across the world are preparing for the Beijing 2022 in full swing on the track. They thumb up for the venue, the test events, and also the excellent performance of themselves. Produced by Xinhua Global Service 